# Project: {{PROJECT_NAME}}

## Overview

This is a **headless Craft CMS + Nuxt** project. Craft CMS serves as the backend CMS (via GraphQL API), and Nuxt provides the frontend (Vue.js SSR/SSG).

- **Backend URL**: {{DDEV_PRIMARY_URL}}
- **Control Panel**: {{DDEV_PRIMARY_URL}}/admin
- **Frontend URL**: http://localhost:3000
- **Environment**: DDEV (backend) + Node.js (frontend)

## Tech Stack

### Backend (Craft CMS)
- **CMS**: Craft CMS 4.x/5.x
- **API**: GraphQL (built-in)
- **PHP Version**: {{DDEV_PHP}}
- **Database**: {{DDEV_DB_TYPE}}/{{DDEV_DB_VERSION}}
- **Environment**: DDEV (Docker-based local dev)

### Frontend (Nuxt)
- **Framework**: Nuxt 3.x
